        {
            "title": "土瓜灣海心公園男子墮海 獲救時昏迷急送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e3baa31bf8bfa8e0d84670562ddb91b4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041623381425436.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>土瓜灣海心公園，今日（4月16日）晚上10時許，有人發現一名男子在離岸3至4米海面載浮載沉，隨即報警求助。警方消防接報趕至將男子救上岸，惜他已陷入昏迷，且無呼吸脈搏，救護員隨即為其安上自動心外壓機，並送往醫院搶救。男子墮海原因仍在調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199576/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"救護員為男子安上自動心外壓機，並送往醫院搶救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/20975892b75682250ef795c370fabf0d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_231954528_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        救護員為男子安上自動心外壓機，並送往醫院搶救。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199577/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"救護員為男子安上自動心外壓機，並送往醫院搶救。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e9eb6f49e5dcfded6364002d390a65ab/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_231954528.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        救護員為男子安上自動心外壓機，並送往醫院搶救。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199580/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員檢查懷疑男子個人物品。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/434d9c60054ef000bdd13d2e4e61cda1/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_232951644_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員檢查懷疑男子個人物品。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199578/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員檢查懷疑男子個人物品。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a2612f4c691c035bc6f27806078fce37/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_232951644_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員檢查懷疑男子個人物品。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199581/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水警輪參與救援。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/66ea4d2cf1f8fae7b74443170d10964c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_232951644_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水警輪參與救援。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4199579/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水警輪參與救援。徐裕民攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/756a0bc522382cbfdb91971f97160786/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_232951644_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水警輪參與救援。徐裕民攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
